 Cuba.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":18.1309,"vote_count":13599,"poster_path":"/hek3koDUyRQk7FIhPXsa6mT2Zc3.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-20","vote_average":8.571,"backdrop_path":"/kGzFbGhp99zva6oZODW5atUtnqi.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":241,"adult":false,"title":"Natural Born Killers","video":false,"overview":"Two victims of traumatized childhoods become lovers and serial murderers irresponsibly glorified by the mass media.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"popularity":4.7277,"vote_count":3702,"poster_path":"/fEKZwT91gxvkAoyPgpNXo8W5fu0.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-26","vote_average":7.052,"backdrop_path":"/k3TOt50cHvTLXWYPnXP0szhiXB8.jpg","original_title":"Natural Born Killers","original_language":"en"},{"id":242,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather Part III","video":false,"overview":"In the midst of trying to legitimize his business dealings in 1979 New York and Italy, aging mafia don, Michael Corleone seeks forgiveness for his sins while taking a young protege under his wing.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":11.3663,"vote_count":6706,"poster_path":"/lm3pQ2QoQ16pextRsmnUbG2onES.jpg","release_date":"1990-12-25","vote_average":7.42,"backdrop_path":"/8zhviPFJx25k8PbUOUL5sLOy9XE.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather Part III","original_language":"en"},{"id":248,"adult":false,"title":"Pocketful of Miracles","video":false,"overview":"A New York gangster and his girlfriend attempt to turn street beggar Apple Annie into a society lady when the peddler learns her daughter is marrying royalty.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":1.1896,"vote_count":178,"poster_path":"/xjXwcGJjT5tE22wazQUYH32HwU8.jpg","release_date":"1961-12-18","vote_average":7.275,"backdrop_path":"/kYaqmkeCSqNSat8nKgdLSz0A20l.jpg","original_title":"Pocketful of Miracles","original_language":"en"},{"id":251,"adult":false,"title":"Ghost","video":false,"overview":"After a young man is murdered, his spirit stays behind to warn his lover of impending danger, with the