 first child, Antoine finds himself enraptured with a young Japanese beauty. The complications change the course of their relationship forever.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.6152,"vote_count":303,"poster_path":"/s9R5wKbrB9SfOG1FzbICbOsssX8.jpg","release_date":"1970-09-09","vote_average":7.097,"backdrop_path":"/9JJqO2yNfoE4uAbu5FDhIhwbqpq.jpg","original_title":"Domicile conjugal","original_language":"fr"},{"id":259,"adult":false,"title":"Love on the Run","video":false,"overview":"Now in his thirties, Antoine Doinel is a divorced proofreader in love with a record seller. Colette Tazzi, now a lawyer, buys his first published autobiography, leading them to a chance meeting.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"popularity":1.3383,"vote_count":210,"poster_path":"/shUrax1ZJXYyclxUaktsTBUHMa9.jpg","release_date":"1979-01-24","vote_average":7.036,"backdrop_path":"/7LmhNfSkSkE296AvQbLZK4jgbnp.jpg","original_title":"L'Amour en fuite","original_language":"fr"},{"id":948276,"adult":false,"title":"Lost Bullet 2","video":false,"overview":"Having cleared his name, genius mechanic Lino has only one goal in mind: getting revenge on the corrupt cops who killed his brother and his mentor.","genre_ids":[28,80,53,18],"popularity":1.0036,"vote_count":467,"poster_path":"/uAeZI1JJbLPq7Bu5dziH7emHeu7.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-10","vote_average":6.498,"backdrop_path":"/707thQazLJiYLBhCrZlRoV05NNL.jpg","original_title":"Balle perdue 2","original_language":"fr"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0074958","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q572165","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/network","mydramalist_id":"17595","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/network"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":111036,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AE","release_dat